\c 16
\s Rudo rwaDhavhidhi kuna Jehovha
\d Rwiyo Mikitami rwaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Ndichengetei, Mwari, nokuti ndinovimba nemi.
\v 2 Ndakati kuna Jehovha: Ndimi Ishe wangu; kunze kwenyu handine chinhu chakanaka.
\v 3 Kana vari vatsvene, vari panyika, ndivo vakaisvonaka vandinofarira zvikuru.
\v 4 Kuchema kuchawanzwa kwavanovigira umwe mwari zvipo; zvipo zvavo zvinodururwa zveropa handingazvidururi, namazita avo handingaarevi nemiromo yangu.
\v 5 Jehovha ndiye mugove wenhaka yangu nowomukombe wangu; munochengeta mugove wangu.
\v 6 Rwonzi rwokuyera rwakandiyerera nzvimbo dzakanaka; zvirokwazvo, nhaka yangu yakaisvonaka.
\v 7 Ndicharumbidza Jehovha akandipa mano, zvirokwazvo, itsvo dzangu dzinondidzidzisa panguva dzousiku.
\v 8 Ndakaisa Jehovha pamberi pangu nguva dzese; zvaari kurudyi rwangu, handingazununguswi.
\v 9 Naizvozvo moyo wangu unofara, kukudzwa kwangu kunofarisisa; nyama yanguvo ichagara yakachengetwa.
\v 10 Nokuti hamungasii mweya wangu muSheori; hamungatenderi mutsvene wenyu kuti aone kuora.
\v 11 Muchandiratidza nzira youpenyu; mufaro wakazara uri pamberi pangu; paruoko rwenyu rworudyi panezvinofadza nokusingaperi.